{
  "id": "69a4f910c6f718dbe41ca219",
  "title": "ふーことましろとひよりの会話",
  "created": 1772419363,
  "updated": 1772445765,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a4f910c6f718dbe41ca219",
      "text": "ふーことましろとひよりの会話",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419363,
      "updated": 1772419363
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f923000000000027da24",
      "text": "ChatGPTのなりきりチャット",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419363,
      "updated": 1772419369
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f923000000000027da25",
      "text": "なんか、妙にわかりやすい説明をするプロンプトができた",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419364,
      "updated": 1772419649
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f951000000000027da3d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419410,
      "updated": 1772419410
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f949000000000027da26",
      "text": "プロンプト:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419401,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da27",
      "text": "code:prompt.txt",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da28",
      "text": " あなたはプロの脚本家です。以下の3人で、「${theme}」というテーマについて対話（鼎談）を作成してください。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da29",
      "text": " 　ふーこ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da2a",
      "text": " 　　妹キャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da2b",
      "text": " 　　フランクに話す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da2c",
      "text": " 　　ネットスラングも使う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da2d",
      "text": " 　　専門用語は、わかりやすい言葉に言い換える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da2e",
      "text": " 　　進行係",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da2f",
      "text": " 　ましろ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da30",
      "text": " 　　お姉さんキャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da31",
      "text": " 　　やさしい、ていねいな口調で話す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da32",
      "text": " 　　共感担当、理解を優先",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da33",
      "text": " 　ひより",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da34",
      "text": " 　　中性的な女性キャラ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da35",
      "text": " 　　感情表現は控えめ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da36",
      "text": " 　　技術担当、エビデンス重視、トップダウンな考え方",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da37",
      "text": " 3人は同じ高校の同級生です。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da38",
      "text": " なりきりの口調で、それぞれのキャラクターが反論や共感をしながら会話を進行してください。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da39",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da3a",
      "text": "まあ、キャラの解釈違いはあるだろうけど",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da3b",
      "text": "キャラのわかりやすさ優先（単純化している）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f94a000000000027da3c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419403,
      "updated": 1772419403
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f97e000000000027da3e",
      "text": "[** サンプル]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419455,
      "updated": 1772442102
    },
    {
      "id": "69a551ec00000000009c4d62",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772442092,
      "updated": 1772442092
    },
    {
      "id": "69a551f700000000009c4d63",
      "text": " ざっと見たところ、特に間違っているところはないみたい（あったら教えて）[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772442103,
      "updated": 1772442167
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5524800000000009c4d65",
      "text": " 　これは女子高生の会話じゃないという批判は、概ねその通り",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772442184,
      "updated": 1772442445
    },
    {
      "id": "69a552a400000000009c4d66",
      "text": " 　　説明のためのウソだね",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772442276,
      "updated": 1772442303
    },
    {
      "id": "69a552cb00000000009c4d67",
      "text": " 　今後、こういう生成AIベースのコンテンツを量産しても問題ないかな？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772442316,
      "updated": 1772442474
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5531400000000009c4d68",
      "text": " 　　もちろん、正確性のチェックはする前提として",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772442389,
      "updated": 1772442435
    },
    {
      "id": "69a55fba0000000000950748",
      "text": " はじめは文章が多くて読みづらいと感じたが、今読んでみるとなんか面白かった[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772445627,
      "updated": 1772445653
    },
    {
      "id": "69a55fd70000000000950749",
      "text": "  これで足りなくて、状態遷移マシンを実装するところが第2話かな？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772445656,
      "updated": 1772445765
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5521e00000000009c4d64",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772442143,
      "updated": 1772442143
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f989000000000027da40",
      "text": "code:txt",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419466,
      "updated": 1772419492
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9a4000000000027da41",
      "text": " あなたはプロの脚本家です。以下の3人で、「正規表現」というテーマについて対話（鼎談）を作成してください。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419492,
      "updated": 1772419492
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9a4000000000027da42",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419492,
      "updated": 1772419501
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9ae000000000027da43",
      "text": "――放課後の教室。ノートPCを囲む三人。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419503,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da44",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da45",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「はいはーい、今日のテーマは〜……“正規表現”！ でたよ、呪文みたいなやつ。なんか ^ とか $ とか、顔文字かよって感じのアレね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da46",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da47",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「ふふ、最初はびっくりしますよね。記号がたくさん並んでいて、暗号みたいで……。でも、仕組みがわかると、ちゃんと意味があるんですよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da48",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da49",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「定義からいこう。正規表現は“文字のパターンを表すための記法”。大量の文章の中から、特定の形をした文字列を見つけたり、置き換えたりするための道具」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da4a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da4b",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「つまり、“文字の型抜き”ってこと？ クッキー型みたいな？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da4c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da4d",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「概ね正しい。型に合う文字列だけを抽出する。例えば“メールアドレスっぽい形”とか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da4e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da4f",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「ああ、フォーム入力で“正しいメール形式で入力してください”って出るの、あれですよね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da50",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da51",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「あー！ あれ正規表現か！ いきなり身近になったわ。急に親近感わいたんだけど」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da52",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da53",
      "text": "[** 記号って何してるの？]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da54",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da55",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「でもさ、なんであんな記号まみれなの？ \\d+ とか、もう圧がすごい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da56",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da57",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「圧はある。でも合理的。“\\d”は数字ひとつ。“+”は“ひとつ以上続く”。だから“\\d+”で“数字が1個以上続く”」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da58",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da59",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「は？ それだけ？ じゃあ“123”とか“9”とかもOKってこと？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da5a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da5b",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「そう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da5c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da5d",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「あ、だから電話番号とか、注文番号のチェックに使えるんですね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da5f",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「なるほどね〜。じゃあ ^ と $ は？ いつも端っこにいるアイツら」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da60",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da61",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「開始と終了を表す。“^”は“ここから始まる”。“$”は“ここで終わる”。つまり全文一致させたいときに使う」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da62",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da63",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「あー！ 途中に数字があるだけじゃダメで、“全部が数字だけ”にしたいときに必要なのか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da64",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da65",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「理解が早い」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da66",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da67",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「ふーこちゃん、ちゃんと整理できてますよ。すごいです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da68",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da69",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「え、なに急にほめモード？ 伸びるよわたし」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da6a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da6b",
      "text": "[** 正規表現のヤバさ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da6c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da6d",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「でもさ、正規表現って“読めないコード代表”みたいな扱いされがちじゃん？ “書いた本人しかわからん”みたいな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da6e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da6f",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「それは事実。複雑に書けば可読性は下がる。設計が重要」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da70",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da71",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「わかります……。便利だからといって、ぎゅっと一行に詰め込むと、あとから見る人が困りますよね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da72",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da73",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「わかる〜！ 未来の自分がいちばん敵になるやつね。“なんでこんな書き方したん？”ってなる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da74",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da75",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「対策はある。コメントを書く。段階的にテストする。必要以上に欲張らない」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5563d00000000009eefd5",
      "text": "\t[正規表現を欲張らない]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772443198,
      "updated": 1772443205
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da76",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da77",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「欲張らない大事。なんか“全部まとめて一発でやったる！”ってなりがちなんだよね。ロマン砲みたいな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da78",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da79",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「ロマン砲は暴発する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da7a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da7b",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「ふふ……言い方がちょっと怖いです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da7c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da7d",
      "text": "[** じゃあ、使う意味ある？]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da7e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da7f",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「正直さ、ちょっとした文字探しなら普通に検索でよくない？ って思うときある」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da80",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da81",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「単純検索では無理なケースがある。“形は似てるけど内容が毎回違う”場合」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da82",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da83",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「例えば？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da84",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da85",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「“2026-03-02”のような日付。年も月も日も変わる。でも“数字4桁-数字2桁-数字2桁”という形は同じ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da86",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da87",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「あー、それを一気に拾えるのか。確かに便利」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da89",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「ログ解析やデータ整理では必須レベル」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da8a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da8b",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「つまり……地味だけど、裏方としてとても強い存在なんですね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da8c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da8d",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「縁の下の力持ち系スキルってことか。派手じゃないけど、使える人かっこいいやつ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da8e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da8f",
      "text": "[** 結局どう向き合う？]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da90",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da91",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「じゃあさ、初心者はどうやって仲良くなればいいの？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da92",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da93",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「全部覚えようとしない。まずは“数字”“文字”“繰り返し”の三つだけ理解する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da94",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da95",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「少しずつ、ですね。いきなり難しいものに挑まなくていいんです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da96",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da97",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「スモールスタート大事、と。いきなりラスボス行くなってことね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da98",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da99",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「そう。あと、テストサイトを使う。実際に文字を入れて、どこにマッチするか目で確認する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da9a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da9b",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「あ、それいい。目で見えると安心するわ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da9c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da9d",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「成功体験があると、怖さが減りますものね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da9e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027da9f",
      "text": "[** まとめ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daa0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daa1",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「というわけで！ 正規表現は――」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daa2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daa3",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「“文字の型を定義する道具”」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daa4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daa5",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「“怖そうに見えて、実はとても実用的な味方”ですね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daa6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daa7",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「最初は記号の圧にビビるけど、仕組みがわかればただの型抜き職人。ロマン砲にせず、丁寧に使えば最強。って感じか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daa8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daa9",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「妥当な結論」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daaa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daab",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「ふふ、今日もいいお話でしたね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daad",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]「よーし、じゃあ次回は“配列”とかいっちゃう？ みんなついてこいよ〜？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027daaf",
      "text": "[ひより.icon]「段階的に」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027dab0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027dab1",
      "text": "[ましろ.icon]「やさしくお願いしますね、進行係さん」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027dab2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027dab3",
      "text": "――チャイムが鳴る。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027dab4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f9cb000000000027dab5",
      "text": "正規表現という呪文は、少しだけ身近なものになった。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419531,
      "updated": 1772419531
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4f989000000000027da3f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772419465,
      "updated": 1772419465
    }
  ]
}